						<summary>

						<p>Slab in the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Vīrōdhi, Vaisākha ba. 10.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the obeisance of Veṅkaṭa Nārāyaṇa Dāsuri son of Tirumalaya of Anantapuram to god Kēśava of Nandēla. In late characters.</p>						

